---
import { Check, FileText, ArrowRight } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 lg:py-28 bg-dark-secondary">
  <!-- Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 dot-pattern opacity-20 pointer-events-none" />
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/3 w-80 h-80 bg-amber/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" />

  <div class="container-main relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <!-- Factura visual -->
      <div class="gsap-scale-in">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 text-zinc-100 border border-zinc-700 shadow-xl">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 border-b border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800/50">
            <span class="label-tag text-zinc-400">FACTURA #001-00000001</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-500/20 border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-full text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold">
              PAGADA
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="p-5 space-y-5">
            <!-- Parties -->
            <div class="flex justify-between text-sm">
              <div>
                <div class="label-tag text-zinc-500 mb-1">EMISOR</div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-200">Mi Negocio C.A.</div>
                <div class="text-zinc-500 nums">RIF J-12345678-9</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="label-tag text-zinc-500 mb-1">CLIENTE</div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-200">Cliente General</div>
                <div class="text-zinc-500 nums">V-12345678</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Items -->
            <div class="border-t border-dashed border-zinc-700 pt-4 space-y-2">
              <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-300">
                <span>1× Harina PAN 1kg</span>
                <span class="nums text-zinc-200">$2.50</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-300">
                <span>2× Aceite Vegetal 1L</span>
                <span class="nums text-zinc-200">$11.60</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-300">
                <span>3× Coca-Cola 600ml</span>
                <span class="nums text-zinc-200">$5.25</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Totals -->
            <div class="border-t-2 border-zinc-700 pt-3 space-y-2">
              <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400">
                <span>Subtotal</span>
                <span class="nums">$19.35</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-zinc-400">
                <span>IVA (16%)</span>
                <span class="nums">$3.10</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between font-bold text-lg pt-2 border-t border-zinc-700">
                <span class="text-zinc-100">Total USD</span>
                <span class="nums text-amber">$22.45</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <div class="px-5 py-3 border-t border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-800/50">
            <span class="label-tag text-zinc-500">TAMBIÉN DISPONIBLE: NIT • RFC • CUIT</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="gsap-fade-up text-zinc-100">
          Facturas que hablan el<br />
          <span class="text-amber">idioma fiscal de tu país.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="gsap-fade-up mt-6 text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-lg leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          RIF, NIT, RFC, RUC o CUIT según tu jurisdicción. IVA e IGV configurables,
          numeración correlativa y notas de crédito con trazabilidad completa.
        </p>

        <ul class="gsap-stagger mt-8 space-y-4">
          {[
            "IVA/IGV configurable por país",
            "RIF, NIT, RFC, RUC, CUIT según país",
            "Facturas, notas de crédito y devoluciones",
            "Numeración correlativa con trazabilidad",
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-zinc-300">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-amber/20 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Check size={12} class="text-amber" />
              </div>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <div class="gsap-fade-up mt-7 p-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 text-sm text-zinc-500 font-mono" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          Gestiona datos formales de facturación — No es un sistema fiscal certificado
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
